        <abstract> 
<p>Is writing confidentially not to justify the passage referred to [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">9759</hi>], which he much regrets, but to state facts. He never intended any personal hostility to [George] Darwin and seeks advice about how to make reparation.</p> 
